#

Stuffed Bell Peppers with Ground Turkey and Rice

45 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyFamily-FriendlyHealthy

Description

Delicious bell peppers filled with savory ground turkey and rice, topped with melted cheese.

Ingredients

  • bell peppers: 4
  • ground turkey: 1 pound
  • cooked rice: 1 cup
  • onion: 1, diced
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • tomato sauce: 1 cup
  • cheddar cheese: 1 cup, shredded
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
